parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag inflator can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the passenger side airbag is deployed without incident or warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag to fail to deploy in a crash, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the passenger side airbag is deployed without incident or warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the SRS unit can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the SRS unit needs to be replaced
the seat belt locking unit needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the engine to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails to start
the ignition switch makes a buzzing sound
the key can be removed while the engine is still running.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the windows can cause inconvenience, discomfort, and safety risks, especially if the windows fail to close properly.
symptoms: The windows fail to open or close
make a clicking sound
or operate erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated
the airbags fail to deploy in an accident
or the passenger airbag is disabled despite having an adult passenger.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various malfunctions, including engine stalling, and increase the risk of accidents or fires.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the radio or other accessories fail to function
or there are signs of electrical burning or smoke.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid battery can cause the vehicle to lose power and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine light is illuminated
the vehicle loses power
or the hybrid battery fails to hold a charge.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause the vehicle to lose power and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
or the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when the vehicle is unable to stop in time.
symptoms: Soft or spongy brake pedal
brake pedal travels lower than normal
uneven brake wear
grinding or loud noise when braking
vibration or wobbling when braking
inability to stop the vehicle
and near accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brake pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake pedal does not return to its normal position
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brake pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake pedal does not return to its normal position
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS modulator can cause the vehicle to lose control, especially when braking on uneven or slippery surfaces, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Vibration or wobbling when braking
inability to stop the vehicle
near accidents
and noise or grinding when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake caliper can cause the brake pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake pedal does not return to its normal position
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.
